# C++ Documentation

## Requirement

All public APIs in C++ code SHALL be documented using Doxygen-style comments.

Documentation SHALL include descriptions for classes, functions, parameters, return values, and exceptions where applicable.

---
description: C++ Doxygen documentation requirement for public APIs
globs: ["*.cpp", "*.hpp", "*.h", "*.cc", "*.cxx", "*.hxx"]
alwaysApply: false
